data.title: Enterprise Analytics
data.meta_description: The Office of Enterprise Analytics provides analytical support for planning and decision-making in the University of Kansas Medical Center (KUMC) and acts as the source for official data about KUMC.
data.text:
The Office of Enterprise Analytics (EA) is dedicated and committed to the faculty and staff at the University of Kansas Medical Center (KUMC), providing for their institutional data, reporting and analytical needs, and assisting leaders with planning and decision-making efforts.

EA offers business intelligence, reporting and advanced analytical solutions related to institutional data (e.g. student and academic programs; faculty and staff; research portfolio; and finance, HR and payroll).

We have excellent, highly experienced, responsive staff with enhanced skills in data mining, custom reporting, pattern recognition, programming, statistical analysis and application development, whose backgrounds stem from academia, data management, finance and accounting.

Please don't hesitate to contact us with your institutional needs.

We look forward to serving you.
